On October 13th 2009, a [[negro|black mailman]], Hugson Jean, delivered a piece of mail to [[white_trash|60 year old]] '''Erika Winchester''' and received a barrage of [[trufax]] about his race.  Lucky enough for the internet, Hugson got it on video.  On November 12th, a year later, the video went viral after Hugson was [[fired]] and uploaded it to youtube.

