== What Happened? ==

When Erika signed a card in the mail (meant for her husband), she then [[I_suck_cocks|changed her mind]] and opened can of [[white power]] whoop ass with a slap to Hugson's face.  After chasing Hugson back to his mail truck she began to demand the card be given back to her.  However, Hugson, having legally stolen the card in the name of USPS, refused to give it back.  As soon as Erika latched onto the car she began to explain to Hugson why [[negro|his race]] is inferior.

