== Previous lols ==
The woman known around town for her [[USI|outbursts]] reportedly was arrested in August 2005 after drunkenly crashing her Volvo into a street sign and subsequently trying to hit one of the paramedics that was treating her. She was arrested again in January 2007 after telling cast members at a community theater rehearsal they would "[[cho|get it with a machine gun,]]" then telling the cop that arrested her for trespassing that she would [[Transgender|"chop off"]] his genitals.

